et=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noopener noreferrer">book</a> is an elegy for a vanish=
ed Central Europe: carved doorways, regional dialects, innkeepers=E2=80=99 =
rituals, bargemen=E2=80=99s songs, and the fading grandeur of an old world =
on the eve of the Second World War.</div><div class=3D"book-of-the-week__bu=
